	    | Do you need "set solib-search-path" or "set sysroot"?
	    | ../../src/gdb/gdbarch.c:3388: internal-error: int gdbarch_elf_make_msymbol_special_p(gdbarch*): Assertion `gdbarch != NULL' failed.
